  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 220\u00136C.",
    "Roll out the pizza dough to a thickness of about 1 cm.",
    "Spread the olive oil evenly over the dough, leaving a 2 cm border around the edges.",
    "Sprinkle the pancetta, bhuna, roma tomatoes, basil, parmesan cheese, and mozzarella cheese over the dough.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Bake the pizza in the preheated oven for 15 minutes.",
    "Remove the pizza from the oven and let it cool for 2 minutes.",
    "Slice the pizza into 8 equal pieces.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
